      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return it to the pot and keep covered until serving&nbsp;</p>",
