    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated onion</strong>, <strong>beef mince</strong> and<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a large bowl&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Crumble the <strong>beef stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into the bowl and knead thoroughly with clean hands for 2-3 min</p>\r\n<p>Once smooth, divide the <strong>mince</strong> into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> and shape into oval-shaped burgers &ndash; these are your <strong>h<strong>ambagu</strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>",
